      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Kath Webster was appointed Director of Scientific Services, APHA in April 2014. She first joined the agency in June 1990.</p>

<p>Her previous roles include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Deputy Chief Scientist, APHA</li>
  <li>Head of Biotechnology and Manager of Test Development Programme, APHA</li>
  <li>Senior Veterinary Research Officer, Parasitology Department</li>
</ul>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_2197">
            <h1 id="director-of-scientific-services">Director of Scientific Services</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director of Scientific Services is responsible for the leadership and management of science delivery across the agency.</p>
</div>
